<HEADLINE> Chinese Leader Thanks Taoists For Flood Donations </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 24 (Xinhua) -- Li Ruihuan, chairman of the
National Committee of the Chinese People's Political Consultative
Conference (CPPCC), today thanked the country's Taoists who have
given a large amount of money for the victims of the recent
floods.
</P>
