<HEADLINE> Italian Investigator to Meet Chelsea's Italians </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, August 24 (Xinhua) -- Chelsea's Italian stars are to
face drug investigation from the Italian Olympic Committee (CONI)
as Italy's top anti-drugs investigator Ugo Longo is set to visit
London for recent drug allegations.
</P>
<P>
