out in Italy.
</P>
<P>
Longo has interviewed a series of top sporting figures this
week.
</P>
<P>
The doping issue emerged when AS Roma coach Zdenek Zeman said
he suspected that many players in the Serie A were using drugs to
build up their bodies. 
