<HEADLINE> Military Generals Pledge Loyalty to President Estrada </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, August 24 (Xinhua) -- Philippine senior military
officials reaffirmed here Monday their unswerving loyalty to
President Joseph Estrada, finally putting to rest rumors of a coup
plot against the Estrada administration.
</P>
<P>
