Philippines will follow all orders of the President being the
Commander-in-Chief, and the Secretary of National Defense. We
pledged to him our loyalty to the Constitution and to the
Commander-in-Chief and informed him that there is no truth to
rumors of a coup d'etat," Nazareno said.
</P>
<P>
