<HEADLINE> Australian Stocks Sharply Down as World Markets Drop </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, August 24 (Xinhua) -- Weakness in key overseas equity
markets and a softening Australian dollar combined to push the
local sharemarket sharply lower Monday.
</P>
<P>
