<HEADLINE> Czech Republic's Skoda Car Exports Up </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PRAGUE, August 23 (Xinhua) -- The Czech Republic's Skoda
company exported 180,300 cars in the first half of this year, up
11.4 percent over the same period of 1997.
</P>
