<HEADLINE> Investment up in China's Western Areas in Jan-Jun </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 24 (Xinhua) -- The latest figures from the
State Statistics Bureau show that investment in China's western
areas hit 81.78 billion yuan in the first six months of 1998, up
20.1 percent over the same period of last year.
</P>
