Standing Committee, praised soliders and police for their
contributions to the fight and said that they should follow
President Jiang Zemin's instructions win the fight.
</P>
<P>
Li Ruihuan, who is Chairman of the Chinese People's Political
Consultative Conference (CPPCC) National Committee, called Inner
Mongolian officials and spoke highly of their flood control effort.
</P>
