<HEADLINE> China's Retail Sales up in Jan-Jun </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 24 (Xinhua) -- China's retail sales amounted
to 1397.9 billion yuan in the first six months of this year, up 6.8
